Class PropPane

  • java.lang.Object

    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SysConfigPane

    public class PropPane
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    The graphic user interface (GUI) component as panel JPanel shows a properties list represented by PropList. It also allows user to modify, save, and load the property list.
    Version:
    10.0
    Author:
    Loc Nguyen
